    <p><anchor n="T.50.2059.0401c12"/><lb ed="T" n="0401c12"/><persName key="A002323">釋道營</persName>，未詳<ptr target="fn24"/>何人。始住<placeName key="PL000000008764">靈曜寺</placeName>習禪，晚<lb ed="T" n="0401c13"/>依<persName key="A001746">觀</persName>、<persName key="A002319">詢</persName>二律師諮受毘尼。偏善《僧祇》一部，<lb ed="T" n="0401c14"/>誦《法華》、《金光明》，蔬素守節。<placeName key="PL000000008702">莊嚴</placeName><persName key="A002255">道慧</persName>、<ptr target="fn25"/><placeName key="PL000000008804">治城</placeName><lb ed="T" n="0401c15"/><persName key="A002270">智秀</persName>，皆師其戒範。<persName key="A002972">張永</persName>請還<placeName key="PL000000009934">吳郡</placeName>，<persName key="A003365">蔡興宗</persName>復<lb ed="T" n="0401c16"/>要住<placeName key="PL000000013417">上虞</placeName>。<persName key="A002972">永</persName>後於<placeName key="PL000000008608">京師婁<ptr target="fn26"/>胡苑</placeName>立<placeName key="PL000000008710">閑心寺</placeName>，<lb ed="T" n="0401c17"/>復請還居。講席頻仍，學徒甚盛。<date key="j18956961896049" from-iso="0478-02-19" to-iso="0479-02-07">昇明二年</date>卒，<lb ed="T" n="0401c18"/>春秋八十有三矣。</p><p>時有<persName key="A003366">釋慧祐</persName>者，本<placeName key="PL000000010993">丹徒</placeName>人，<lb ed="T" n="0401c19"/>年三十出家。厲身苦節，精尋律教。<date key="j18961391904532" notAfter-iso="0502" notBefore-iso="0479">齊</date>初入<lb ed="T" n="0401c20"/>東<ptr target="fn27"/>山講《摩訶僧祇部》。<persName key="A002655">齊竟陵王子良</persName>遣迎<lb ed="T" n="0401c21"/>出<placeName key="PL000000008975">都</placeName>，仍止<placeName key="PL000000008710">閑心寺</placeName>焉。</p>
